Title: Form Engine .NET
Description:
Form Engine is an online service that meshes the presentation of HTML forms with the 
portability of PDF documents. HTML forms, automatically generated from a PDF document, are used to gather data from end-users. This data is then merged into the 
associated PDF document.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
Form Engine is an online service that meshes the presentation of HTML forms with the
portability of PDF documents. HTML forms, automatically generated from a PDF document, are used to gather data from end-users. This data is then merged into the
associated PDF document.

Further information can be found at http://formengine.auburnrandall.com
